description:
C O D E X
P R E S E N T S

NARUTO SHIPPUDEN: Ultimate Ninja STORM 2 (c) BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment
Release Date: 08/2017 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Action
NARUTO SHIPPUDEN: Ultimate Ninja STORM 2 is a tour de force of
Naruto thrills and spills. Impressively faithful to the universe of
the anime, the game takes players through the Naruto Shippuden
story arc with new battle systems enhancing the gameplay. Players
must choose the right companions to fight alongside and together
unleash explosive Team Special Techniques to lay waste to
opponents
